President Obama announced his intent to nominate several individuals to key administration posts. These include Alan F. Estevez as Principal Deputy Under Secretary of Defense for Acquisition, Technology, and Logistics at the Department of Defense, Vincent G. Logan as Special Trustee for American Indians at the Department of the Interior, and Olga Viso as a member of the National Council on the Arts. President Obama also announced his intent to appoint individuals to key administration posts, such as Jean Bahr as a member of the Nuclear Waste Technical Review Board and Steven M. Becker as a member of the same board. The article provides brief backgrounds on each nominee.